===Noun===
'''weather'''

# the short term state of the [[atmosphere]] at a [[specific]] [[time]] and [[place]], including the [[temperature]], [[humidity]], [[cloud]] [[cover]]age and [[fall]] of [[precipitation]], [[wind]], etc.
# [[unpleasant]] or [[destructive]] [[atmospheric]] [[condition]]s, and its [[effect]]s

